### Create user (ownerId is set on server side)
# 日本語メモ: ownerIdは送らず、サーバ側でme.idを入れる
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
x-user-id: 1
x-user-role: ADMIN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hanako",
  "email": "hanako+{{$timestamp}}@example.com"
}

### List users (requires auth headers)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users
x-user-id: 1
x-user-role: ADMIN

### Invalid input (empty name -> 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
x-user-id: 1
x-user-role: ADMIN
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "", "email": "bad@example.com" }

### Duplicate email (-> 409)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
x-user-id: 1
x-user-role: ADMIN
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Hanako", "email": "hanako@example.com" }
